supportDesc.extent: i, 87, leaves : 220 x 110 (155 x 70) mm bound to 220 x 115 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Foliated in ink, upper left recto; catchwords each leaf, lower left verso. Two leaves at the end are bound out of order; foliation as bound: 1-79, 83-84, 81-82, 85-87.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in naskh script in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Tables, diagrams and rubrications in red.

binding.p: Reddish leather over pasteboard (Type III); red paper doublure.
